name: places/ChIJKSw8ep8Z2jERq02DQye5Hv0/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSURoMy03OFlnEAE
text: {'text': 'So safe that I went on it twice when I lived in Singapore. The first time is way to exciting especially as the carriage rolls and moves in a different direction before your eyes tell your brain you are going in that direction. You also then go upwards or downwards at an incredible speed.\nI have seen people pass away during this ride, it is quite common for some. You get back safely on the ground at which point you can get out of the carriage.\nAlso, do not listen to the countdown. It is never the same as launch. Have fun!', 'languageCode': 'en'}
